| Aspect      | Synchronous                                       | Asynchronous                                            |
| ----------- | ------------------------------------------------- | ------------------------------------------------------- |
| Execution   | Blocking; waits for completion distantjob​        | Non-blocking; continues immediately distantjob​         |
| Performance | Slower for multiple I/O operations mendix​        | Faster for I/O-heavy tasks mendix​                      |
| Use Case    | Simple scripts with few operations geeksforgeeks​ | Web servers or apps needing concurrency geeksforgeeks​  |
| Complexity  | Easier to code and debug distantjob​              | Requires handling callbacks or async patterns ramotion​ |
